data.description: Welcome to your home! This fenced property offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and entertainment in a family-friendly neighborhood. With an emphasis on outdoor enjoyment and proximity to schools, this residence is sure to capture your heart. Spacious backyard living with many amenities to entertain your guests. Also included in the back yard is a small shed for storage. Far enough from the noisy roads, but close enough to nearby stores, restaurants, etc. Schedule a showing to see this one in PTISD!
